How to Make a Doginals Wallet

1. Go to doggy.market and create a new wallet, write down the seed phrase on a piece of paper and keep it in a safe place, then backup the wallet!

2. Create a password for the wallet (this will save to your local machine).

3. Once your wallet is created, you can generate a receiving address.

4. You are now ready to send and receive Doge tokens and interact with Doginals on the Doge Blockchain.
